Bilbo is held captive in a cell in the dungeons of Goblin-town.
You hear Bilbo speaking to his captor in the dungeons!
You are very near to rescuing Bilbo from Goblin-town, you can sense it!

Rukzot and his minions stand between you and Bilbo's freedom!
Now that you have the key to Bilbo's cell, you can free him from his captivity.
